REGISTRATION THROUGH ROSBAG:
ros2 bag record <topics name>

---

IN ORDER TO VISUALIZE DATA:
rqt_graph

---

ROSBAG TO CSV CONVERSION:

PLAY ROSBAGS:
cd <path-to-the-rosbag-directories>
ros2 bag play <rosbag directory name> --start-paused

IN OTHER TERMINALS LAUNCH ROS2 TOPIC ECHO RECORDING DATA IN A CSV FILE (ONE TERMINAL FOR EACH TOPIC AS ONE CSV FILE FOR EACH TOPIC):
ros2 topic echo <topic name> > <csv file name>.csv

RESUME PLAYING IN THE FIRST TERMINAL

---
